tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE property_prices (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  property_address VARCHAR,
  price DECIMAL,
  date_recorded DATE,
  UNIQUE (property_address, date_recorded)
)

CREATE TABLE property_transactions (
    transaction_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    property_id UUID,
    buyer_id UUID,
    seller_id UUID,
    transaction_date DATE
);
